{{Talk | Conference=SMWCon Fall 2012 | Title=SMW in Wikia | Description= Experience using SMW in the biggest wiki farm in the world | Start=25 Oct 2012 12:00 | End=25 Oct 2012 12:30 | Duration=30 minutes | Type=Presentation | Audience=Everyone | Slides=20121025 SMWCon Fall Krzysztof Krzyżaniak SMW in Wikia.pdf | Speakers=Krzysztof Krzyżaniak | Attendees= }}
The Semantic MediaWiki Suite are optional extensions which can be enabled on the Wikia platform. Currently more than 150 wikis have these extensions enabled and use them in various ways. Some wikis use Semantic MediaWiki as a better categorization method, others use it as a structured page builder. My short presentation will demonstrate how Semantic Mediawiki is used on Wikia wikis, what problems we have with them and how we handle the issues.
